; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the error when some postings have null amounts after balancing.
; An unbalanced virtual posting with no amount cannot be filled in
; by finalize(), causing the "null amounts after balancing" error.

2024/03/01 Test
    Expenses:Food     $10.00
    Assets:Cash      $-10.00
    (Virtual:Account)

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 9:
Error: There cannot be null amounts after balancing a transaction
end test
